  <title>Fixed Width Add-in</title>
    <p>The <app>Fixed Width</app> add-in allows text to use a fixed width font. To change existing text, first select the text you want to modify. Then select <gui>Fixed Width</gui> from the <gui>Text</gui> menu. You can also select <gui>Fixed Width</gui> from the menu before you start typing.</p>

